    Expected Columns for Individual MDUFA Datasets

    mdufa_cols.Rd

    Column names in the expected order for mdufa2, mdufa3, mdufa4, and mdufa5 datasets. Report metadata columns come first, followed by table location, then metric data.

    mdufa_cols

    Format

    Character vector of 14 column names

    Examples

    # Check if a dataset has expected columns
identical(names(mdufa4), mdufa_cols)
#> [1] TRUE

# Reorder columns to standard order
mdufa4[, mdufa_cols]
